== 防灾措施和影响 ==
确认东大西洋形成飓风后，美国国家气象局向气旋预计行經路径上的船只发布警告<ref name="Warnings Up">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Warnings Up | accessdate = 2017-02-11 | newspaper = The Montreal Gazette | date = 1957-09-06 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ppgtAAAAIBAJ&sjid=eZkFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2927,1021078&dq=hurricane&hl=en | agency = Associated Press | location = San Juan, Puerto Rico | page = 1 | archive-date = 2021-10-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211010143134/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=ppgtAAAAIBAJ&sjid=eZkFAAAAIBAJ&pg=2927%2C1021078&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。面对恶劣海况威胁，[[罗德岛州|罗德岛州]][[布洛克岛|布洛克岛]]（{{lang|en|Block Island}}）向南至[[乔治亚州|乔治亚州]][[萨凡纳|萨凡纳]]近海地区于9月7日收到小型船只警告<ref name="Heads North">{{cite news | title = Big Hurricane Is Far Out In Atlantic; Storm Heads North | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Lk8mAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Xv8FAAAAIBAJ&pg=2534,3384456&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2017-02-11 | newspaper = Gettysburg Times | date = 1957-09-07 | agency = Associated Press | location = Miami, Florida | page = 4 | archive-date = 2021-12-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211221051531/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=Lk8mAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Xv8FAAAAIBAJ&pg=2534%2C3384456&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。9月11日，风暴移动速度大幅放缓，美国国家气象局认为[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]有可能受到气旋影响，但几率很低<ref name="Slight">{{cite news | title = Forecasters Allow Carrie 'Slight Chance' at Florida | newspaper = The Victoria Advocate | accessdate = 2017-02-11 | date = 1957-09-11 | agency = Associated Press | location = Miami, Florida | page = 1 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=E6xTAAAAIBAJ&sjid=EogDAAAAIBAJ&pg=1769,1158738&dq=hurricane&hl=en | archive-date = 2021-12-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211221032748/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=E6xTAAAAIBAJ&sjid=EogDAAAAIBAJ&pg=1769%2C1158738&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。嘉莉转向北上后，气象机构认为飓风基本不可能袭击[[佛罗里达半岛|佛罗里达半岛]]<ref name="Gains">{{cite news | title = Carrie Gains In Intensity | newspaper = The Victoria Advocate | date = 1957-09-12 | agency = Associated Press | location = Miami, Florida | page = 1}}</ref>。气象部门接下来又认为嘉莉可能会吹袭百慕大，岛上学校因此关闭，船只也收到飓风来袭的警告<ref name="RemainSea">{{cite news | title = Hurricane "Carrie" May Remain At Sea | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=8UcpAAAAIBAJ&sjid=LWgFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4992,1470460&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2017-02-11 | newspaper = The Lewiston Daily Sun | date = 1957-09-16 | agency = Associated Press | location = Miami, Florida | page = 1 | archive-date = 2021-10-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211010092629/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=8UcpAAAAIBAJ&sjid=LWgFAAAAIBAJ&pg=4992%2C1470460&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[金德利空军基地|金德利空军基地]]大部分飞机转移，留在基地的飞机则用[[沙袋|沙袋]]固定<ref name="Washington">{{cite news | title = Hurricane Carrie Hits Bermuda | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=NRxiAAAAIBAJ&sjid=p3UNAAAAIBAJ&pg=5462,1312073&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2017-02-11 | newspaper = The Washington Reporter | date = 1957-09-16 | agency = United Press | location = Hamilton Bermuda | page = 5 | archive-date = 2021-10-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211010072613/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=NRxiAAAAIBAJ&sjid=p3UNAAAAIBAJ&pg=5462%2C1312073&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。风暴绕过百慕大后，气象机构预计嘉莉会登陆[[新斯科舍|新斯科舍]]<ref name="NovaScotia">{{cite news | title = Nova Scotia Expects Carrie to Hit | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=dCpgAAAAIBAJ&sjid=V28NAAAAIBAJ&pg=5561,2257880&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2017-02-11 | newspaper = Saskatoon Star-Phoenix | date = 1957-09-18 | agency = The Canadian Press | location = [[哈利法克斯|Halifax, Nova Scotia]] | page = 6 | archive-date = 2021-10-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211010092654/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=dCpgAAAAIBAJ&sjid=V28NAAAAIBAJ&pg=5561%2C2257880&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但气旋实际上转向东北，没有对当地构成影响<ref name="HURDAT" />。

美国空军此时持续派出改装后的[[B-50超级堡垒轰炸机|B-50超级堡垒轰炸机]]飞入飓风侦察，其中一架飞机因发动机失灵被迫返回[[西棕榈滩|西棕榈滩]]维修。另外四架飞机也被召回西棕榈滩，虽然四架飞机都没有受到损伤，但依然有一架不能使用，其余两架则在百慕大停留。<ref name="Peril">{{cite news | title = Carrie Poses Peril To Bermuda | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=HQIdAAAAIBAJ&sjid=1YoEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7306,1201001&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2017-02-11 | newspaper = Sarasota Journal | date = 1957-09-13 | agency = Associated Press | location = Miami, Florida | page = 5 | archive-date = 2021-05-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210512084441/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=HQIdAAAAIBAJ&sjid=1YoEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7306%2C1201001&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>9月16日，嘉莉从百慕大以北较远处海域经过<ref name="MWR" />，岛上所受影响很小，最强阵风时速仅有56公里<ref name="New">{{cite news | title = New Tropical Storm Picks Up Force | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5mAuAAAAIBAJ&sjid=89kFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3933,2253733&dq=hurricane&hl=en | accessdate = 2017-02-11 | newspaper = Beaver Valley Times | date = 1957-09-18 | agency = United Press | location = New Orleans, Louisiana | page = 1 | archive-date = 2021-05-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210512084441/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=5mAuAAAAIBAJ&sjid=89kFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3933%2C2253733&dq=hurricane&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

载有[[大麦|大麦]]、从[[布宜诺斯艾利斯|布宜诺斯艾利斯]]出发前往[[汉堡|汉堡]]的德国“帕米尔号”（{{lang|en|Pamir}}）[[三桅帆船|三桅帆船]]于9月21日在[[亚速尔群岛|亚速尔群岛]]西南方向遇到飓风<ref name="Dwindle">{{cite news | title = Hope Dwindles for German Sailing | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=LAVPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=7UsDAAAAIBAJ&pg=2852,3222690&dq=pamir&hl=en | accessdate = 2017-02-11 | newspaper = Ellensburg Daily Record | date = 1957-09-20 | agency = Associated Press | location = London | page = 1 | archive-date = 2021-12-21 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211221043506/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=LAVPAAAAIBAJ&sjid=7UsDAAAAIBAJ&pg=2852%2C3222690&dq=pamir&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>，全部86人中有80人随船葬身大海<ref name="MWR" />。该船最后发出的[[求救信号|求救信号]]表明所有船帆都已失落，船体倾角达到45°<ref name="Presume">{{cite news | location = London | title = Presume Sailing Ship With 86 Aboard Lost | newspaper = Park City Daily News | date = 1957-09-20 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=JuUcAAAAIBAJ&sjid=zEUEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7103,2278469&dq=pamir&hl=en | accessdate = 2016-02-11 | agency = Associated Press | page = 5 | archive-date = 2021-10-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211010074234/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=JuUcAAAAIBAJ&sjid=zEUEAAAAIBAJ&pg=7103%2C2278469&dq=pamir&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。美国空军、[[美国海军|海军]]，以及[[英国皇家空军|英国皇家空军]]和[[英国皇家海军|海军]]在“帕米尔号”失踪后开展[[搜索及拯救|搜救]]，另外还有[[加拿大|加拿大]]和[[葡萄牙|葡萄牙]]的船只加入搜救<ref name="Lifeboats and Raft">{{cite news | title = 2 Lifeboats, Raft Found In Atlantic | date = 1957-09-21 | agency = Associated Press | location = London | page = 2 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=rCU_AAAAIBAJ&sjid=FFAMAAAAIBAJ&pg=3393,5800192&dq=pamir&hl=en | accessdate = 2017-02-11 | newspaper = The Windsor Daily Star | archive-date = 2021-10-10 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211010092630/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=rCU_AAAAIBAJ&sjid=FFAMAAAAIBAJ&pg=3393,5800192&dq=pamir&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。各国的搜救和调查都没有定论，未能寻获任何船骸<ref name="Dwindle" />；虽然找到两艘[[救生艇|救生艇]]和一条木筏，但上面都没有幸存者<ref name="Lifeboats and Raft" />。嘉莉在转变成温带风暴后吹袭亚速尔群岛，但破坏情况缺乏记载。气旋残留之后又在9月24至25日袭击不列颠群岛，产生狂风巨浪并引发严重洪灾。<ref name="MWR" />估计风速达到每小时80公里，造成大面积地区财物受损，还有三人丧生<ref name="World">{{cite news | title = World Briefs | agency = Associated Press | location = London | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=R581AAAAIBAJ&sjid=4qsFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3106,7291209&dq=carrie+britain&hl=en | accessdate = 2017-02-11 | newspaper = The Owosso Argus-Press | date = 1957-09-25 | page = 21 | archive-date = 2021-05-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210512084428/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=R581AAAAIBAJ&sjid=4qsFAAAAIBAJ&pg=3106%2C7291209&dq=carrie+britain&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 纪录 ==
嘉莉作为热带气旋的时间长达20.75天，刷新历史上持续时间第三长的北大西洋热带气旋纪录，仅次于[[1899年圣奇里亚科飓风|1899年圣奇里亚科飓风]]和[[1926年大西洋飓风季|1926年]]的第四号飓风<ref name="Last">{{cite web | title = Subject: E6) Which tropical cyclone lasted the longest? | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/E6.html | work = Tropical Cyclones Records | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's Hurricane Research Division | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170125054441/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/E6.html | accessdate = 2017-02-11 | last1 = Dorst | first1 = Neal | author2 = Atlantic Oceanographic Meteorological Laboratory | location = Miami, Florida | date = 2016-06-01 | archivedate = 2017-01-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。风暴的持续时间很长，美国国家气象局驻[[圣胡安_(波多黎各)|圣胡安]]办事处共发出62份公告，数量之多创下大西洋飓风新纪录<ref name="Climatological Data">{{cite journal | last1 = Weeks | first1 = Sinclair | last2 = Reichelderfer | first2 = F.W. | title = Annual Summary 1957 | journal = Climatological Data – Alabama | year = 1958 | volume = 44 | issue = 13 | pages = 104–105 | accessdate = 2017-02-11 | publisher = University of Michigan | location = Asheville, North Carolina | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=SSvOAAAAMAAJ&pg=PA101&lpg=PA101&dq=hurricane+carrie+1957+advisories&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q=hurricane%20carrie%201957%20advisories&f=false | archive-date = 2021-05-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210512084513/https://books.google.com/books?id=SSvOAAAAMAAJ&pg=PA101&lpg=PA101&dq=hurricane+carrie+1957+advisories&hl=zh-CN#v=onepage&q=hurricane%20carrie%201957%20advisories&f=false | dead-url = no }}</ref>。持续时间超长的同时，气旋又自始至终远离大陆，所以行进距离长达9700公里，刷新又一项纪录<ref name="MWR" />，直到[[1966年大西洋飓风季|1966年]]才被[[飓风费斯|飓风费斯]]以11020公里打破<ref>{{cite report | last1 = Dorst | first1 = Neal | last2 = Delgado | first2 = Sandy | date = 2011-05-20 | title = Subject: E7) What is the farthest a tropical cyclone has traveled? | publisher = Atlantic Oceanographic and Meteorological Laboratory | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/E7.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170125054446/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/tcfaq/E7.html | location = Miami, Florida | accessdate = 2017-02-11 | archivedate = 2017-01-25 | deadurl = no}}</ref>。风暴远离陆地还令飓风猎人侦察机向东面飞行的距离创下新纪录。9月7日启航的第一架飞机就连续飞行近17小时，航程达6000公里。<ref name="MWR" />

